722697f-a.title: Manhattan: Riverside Drive - 73rd Street
722697f-a.text:
Riverside Drive, north from and including 73rd Street, as seen
from the park on the west side of the ''drive''.
March 29, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

722698f-a.title: Manhattan: Riverside Drive - 73rd Street
722698f-a.text:
21 Riverside Drive, east side, from West 73rd to 74th Streets, showing
the residence of Charles M. Schwab, steel magnate. This structure and
the surrounding grounds occupy the entire block between the Drive and
West End Ave., north from 73rd to 74th Streets. The photographer is
viewing northeastward from 73rd Street (foreground) and the Drive (left,
not shown).
About 1920.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
